Sean Moss - HW4 - CSCI 4229/5229


Controls
========

Arrow Keys - Rotate the camera around the scene, in target camera mode.
-/=        - Zoom the camera in and out from the origin, in target camera mode.
0          - Reset the camera view.
W/S        - Move forward/backward in fps camera mode.
A/D        - Rotate left/right in fps camera mode.
Q/E        - Rotate up/down in fps camera mode.
1/2/3      - Switch between the different camera modes.
Escape     - Exit the application.


This project took me about 4.5 hours to complete, with a good portion of that time
going into adding the code to control the FPS camera.
